made general comments.  
</p>
<p>24. Also at the same meeting, the draft resolution was adopted without a vote. For the 
text of the resolution as adopted, see chapter I. 
</p>
<p><b> H. Selection and appointment of mandate holders 
</b></p>
<p>25. At its 2nd meeting, on 20 January 2014, the Human Rights Council appointed the 
Independent Expert on<b> </b>the situation of human rights in the Central African Republic in 
accordance with Council resolutions 5/1 and 16/21 and its decision 6/102 (see annex II).  
</p>
